        "Title": "Mission Impossible : ICA vs NSA",
        "Location": "LOCATION_WET_RAT",
        "PublicId": "130206078281",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/wet/scene_rat_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 138078d6-0e9f-4e27-8ffb-373d6bbc6b62).Image",
        "Description": "Hello there 47.\r\rFive former CIA NOC agents implicated in a mass murder in Afghanistan have been spotted in China. Our client, an important NGO affiliated with Amnesty International wants Justice to be given. These targets are now NSA contractor in mission, and another crime is planned... Time is ticking before they act.\r\rYour mission, should you choose to accept it, is to eliminate the targets by any means necessary, without compromising the ICA.\r\rTake precautions. Good hunting, 47.",
